Standard and Poor's Corp said it cut toCCC from B-minus International Rectifier Corp's 58 mln dlrs ofconvertible subordinated debentures due 2010.    The company's implied senior debt rating is B-minus.    S and P said the downgrade reflected expectations ofrestricted financial flexibility through at least theintermediate term. It also cited a highly leveraged balancesheet and reduced access to capital.    The rating agency said International Rectifier's ability toreduce high debt levels and interest expense through cash fromoperations is very limited. Reuter&#3;